    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建立你的王国</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Night Keep》是一款受《Thronefall》启发的极简策略砍杀游戏。白天，你建设王国；夜幕降临时，你要利用防御塔、部队以及英雄技能守护它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/80533ca725e4655a0fc8d58b7f4166f2.poster.avif?t=1772359751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/80533ca725e4655a0fc8d58b7f4166f2.webm?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/80533ca725e4655a0fc8d58b7f4166f2.mp4?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平衡经济与防御</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Night Keep》剥离了冗余复杂性，却依旧充满挑战，鼓励玩家制定自己的策略。从多种建筑中进行选择，每座建筑都拥有独特能力和升级路径，在每一关找到经济与防御的最佳平衡。建造房屋、风车和田地，只要它们撑过黑夜就能产出金币，但别太贪心。投入资源升级拥有三条分支的防御塔，或建造兵营招募布偶大军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/79e34b4bf01cef91f0180b64d387c6e5.poster.avif?t=1772359751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/79e34b4bf01cef91f0180b64d387c6e5.webm?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/79e34b4bf01cef91f0180b64d387c6e5.mp4?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择职业并与布娃娃战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供三种职业，每种职业都拥有两项独特技能。你可以同时使用三种职业，并在战斗中无缝切换。挥刀劈砍，迎战二十种不同的布偶敌人。每关开始前，通过选择特权与挑战来自定义你的战斗风格。游戏包含七个关卡，总计约 5-8 小时流程，并提供更高难度和无尽模式，助你挑战全新高分。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/0230e76f6d3c3198ddeac2d49571e8d6.poster.avif?t=1772359751\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/0230e76f6d3c3198ddeac2d49571e8d6.webm?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089580/extras/0230e76f6d3c3198ddeac2d49571e8d6.mp4?t=1772359751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 三种可玩职业</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 七个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 13 种建筑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 20 种独特敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 普通、困难、无尽模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 每关 2 个任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 排行榜系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 15 种特权与 10 种挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 以第三人称或固定俯视视角进行游戏</p>",
